org.agorava.api.oauth

Class OAuthSession

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.agorava.api.oauth.OAuthSession
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Identifiable

    public class OAuthSession
extends Object
implements Identifiable
    Contains user data for a session connection to a given OAuthService. It completes data in OAuthAppSettings. More over it contains status and basic user data when OAuth connexion has been completed
    Author:
    Antoine Sabot-Durand
